title: Scrumptious Stuffed Celery
summary: You can never have too many side dish recipes, so give Scrumptious Stuffed Celery a try. One portion of this dish contains about 1g of protein, 2g of fat, and a total of 75 calories. This recipe serves 6 and costs 46 cents per serving. 1 person were impressed by this recipe. Head to the store and pick up celery stalks, cheddar classic melts cheddar & american, oscar mayer sandwich spread, and a few other things to make it today. It is a good option if you're following a gluten free and vegetarian diet. From preparation to the plate, this recipe takes roughly 5 minutes. With a spoonacular score of 20%, this dish is not so tremendous. Similar recipes include Scrumptious Stuffed Shells, Mamas Stuffed Celery, and Crab-Stuffed Celery.
instructions: Spoon sandwich spread evenly into hollow centers of celery stalks; sprinkle with cheese.                                            Cut each stalk crosswise into 3 pieces.                                              Serve immediately. Or, cover and refrigerate up to 2 hours before serving.
